IT IS NOT CLEAR AT THIS MOMENT

01:26.820 --> 01:27.955
WHETHER THE U.S. HAS BEEN

01:27.955 --> 01:29.289
INVOLVED BUT WE KNOW THEY HAVE

01:29.289 --> 01:30.991
BEEN INVOLVED IN A LOT OF THE

01:30.991 --> 01:32.125
OTHER AIR STRIKES GOING ON

01:32.125 --> 01:33.226
AROUND THAT AREA AND I THINK IT

01:33.226 --> 01:35.162
IS EXPECTED THESE WERE U.S.

01:35.162 --> 01:35.395
STRIKES.

01:35.395 --> 01:35.862
>> Sreenivasan: WHAT DO WE

01:35.862 --> 01:39.933
KNOW ABOUT THE AREA WHERE THE

01:39.933 --> 01:41.034
MOST RECEIPT MASSACRE OCCURRED?

01:41.034 --> 01:44.504
>> THIS IS A SMALL VILLAGE

01:44.504 --> 01:47.140
SOUTHEAST OF SIN JAR, THE

01:47.140 --> 01:48.408
ASSAULT ON THE YEZIDIS A COUPLE

01:48.408 --> 01:51.144
OF WEEKS AGO TRIGGERED THIS

01:51.144 --> 01:51.278
CRISIS.

01:51.278 --> 01:53.680
IT’S IN A VERY SMALL VILLAGE, A

01:53.680 --> 01:54.948
REMOTE AREA.

01:54.948 --> 01:56.416
REPORTS HAVE BEEN SKETCHY BUT WE

01:56.416 --> 01:58.585
KNOW AT ABOUT 1:00 YESTERDAY

01:58.585 --> 02:00.520
FIGHTERS WITH THE ISLAMIC STATE

02:00.520 --> 02:02.222
DID GO INTO THAT VILLAGE AND

02:02.222 --> 02:03.056
THEY APPARENTLY KILLED-- WE HAVE

02:03.056 --> 02:05.625
A NUMBER OF 84 MEN.

02:05.625 --> 02:07.127
THEY LINED THEM UP AND EXECUTED

02:07.127 --> 02:09.096
THEM AND THEY TOOK AWAY AROUND

02:09.096 --> 02:09.496
300 WOMEN.

02:09.496 --> 02:10.263
>> Sreenivasan: IS THERE ANY

02:10.263 --> 02:11.498
CONNECTION BETWEEN THE TIMING OF

02:11.498 --> 02:12.299
WHEN PRESIDENT OBAMA SAID THAT

02:12.299 --> 02:14.334
THE HUMANITARIAN OPERATIONS ON

02:14.334 --> 02:16.303
THE MOUNTAIN ARE DONE?

02:16.303 --> 02:17.771
>> THE SITUATION ON THE MOUNTAIN

02:17.771 --> 02:19.940
HAS GREATLY IMPROVED.

02:19.940 --> 02:20.741
>> Sreenivasan: AND WHEN THESE

02:20.741 --> 02:22.776
PEOPLE WENT IN FOR THE MASSACRE?

02:22.776 --> 02:24.644
>> Reporter: YES, THAT’S WHAT

02:24.644 --> 02:27.147
A LOT OF YEZIDIS AND SOME KURDS

02:27.147 --> 02:28.248
ARE TELL US.

02:28.248 --> 02:29.649
THEY BELIEVE IT’S A DIRECT

02:29.649 --> 02:30.250
CONNECTION BETWEEN PRESIDENT

02:30.250 --> 02:31.818
OBAMA CALLING OFF THE

02:31.818 --> 02:33.620
HUMANITARIAN AIR LIFT OF YEZIDIS

02:33.620 --> 02:34.988
WHICH HAD BEEN PLANNED IN THE

02:34.988 --> 02:35.922
MOUNTAIN NEARBY AND THE ISLAMIC

02:35.922 --> 02:37.024
STATE FIGHTERS GOING IN AND

02:37.024 --> 02:38.125
KILLING THESE PEOPLE.

02:38.125 --> 02:39.993
THEY HAD BEEN SURROUNDING THESE

02:39.993 --> 02:41.461
PEOPLE FAIR WEEK, DEMANDING THEY

02:41.461 --> 02:42.896
CONVERT OR RISK DEATH.

02:42.896 --> 02:43.897
SO IT COULD BE THAT THEY WERE

02:43.897 --> 02:45.465
PLANNING TO GO IN ANYWAY, BUT A

02:45.465 --> 02:47.801
LOT OF PEOPLE FEEL THAT WAS A

02:47.801 --> 02:48.769
SENSE THAT THEY WERE OFF THE

02:48.769 --> 02:50.871
HOOK, A GREEN LIGHT, IF YOU

02:50.871 --> 02:52.672
LIKE, FROM PRESIDENT OBAMA TO

02:52.672 --> 02:54.341
CONTINUE KILLING IN THE AREA.

02:54.341 --> 02:55.609
>> Sreenivasan: HAVE THEY MADE

02:55.609 --> 02:56.476
MORE ADVANCED IN THE REGION

02:56.476 --> 02:57.844
SINCE THE HUMORITARIAN CRISIS

02:57.844 --> 02:59.212
THAT REALLY OCCUPIED MOST OF OUR

02:59.212 --> 03:01.782
HEADLINES HERE IN THE WEST?

03:01.782 --> 03:03.316
>> Reporter: THEY HAVE BEEN

03:03.316 --> 03:04.117
CONTINUING TO ADVANCE THROUGHOUT

03:04.117 --> 03:04.751
THIS TIME.

03:04.751 --> 03:05.552
THEY NEVER REALLY STOPPED.

03:05.552 --> 03:08.021
THE AIR STRIKES DID HELP THEM ON

03:08.021 --> 03:12.692
THE OUTSKIRT OFS OF ERBIL BUT

03:12.692 --> 03:16.663
THEY MADE GAINS DOWN NEAR THE

03:16.663 --> 03:17.664
IRANIAN BORDER, AND THEY’VE BEEN

03:17.664 --> 03:19.800
MAKING A LOT OF GAINS RECENTLY

03:19.800 --> 03:22.769
IN THE NORTHERN ALEPPO COUNTRY,

03:22.769 --> 03:24.104
IN SYRIA, A FURTHER EDGE OF THE

03:24.104 --> 03:25.572
AREA THEY CONTROL.

03:25.572 --> 03:26.673
THEY’VE BEEN TAKING A LOT OF

03:26.673 --> 03:28.175
SMALL TOWNS AND VILLAGES AROUND

03:28.175 --> 03:29.476
ALEPPO IN THE PAST FEW DAYS, AND

03:29.476 --> 03:31.311
PEOPLE ARE VERY AFRAID THAT THE

03:31.311 --> 03:32.579
SYRIAN REBELS THERE ARE GOING TO

03:32.579 --> 03:34.581
LOSE CONTROL OF THE BORDER WITH

03:34.581 --> 03:36.349
TURKEY AND PERHAPS THE TOWN OF

03:36.349 --> 03:36.716
ALEPPO ITSELF.

03:36.716 --> 03:37.984
>> Sreenivasan: WHAT ABOUT THE

03:37.984 --> 03:39.686
TALK THAT PERHAPS THE U.S.

03:39.686 --> 03:41.221
MILITARY AID COULD COME TO

03:41.221 --> 03:42.756
KURDISTAN OR OTHER EUROPEAN

03:42.756 --> 03:44.958
COUNTRIES COULD ASSIST IN THIS

03:44.958 --> 03:45.125
FIGHT?

03:45.125 --> 03:46.393
>> Reporter: WELL, IT’S MY

03:46.393 --> 03:48.161
UNDERSTANDING THAT U.S. MILITARY

03:48.161 --> 03:50.097
AID HAS ALREADY ARRIVED IN

03:50.097 --> 03:50.263
KURDISTAN.

03:50.263 --> 03:51.164
IT WAS ANNOUNCED EARLIER THIS

03:51.164 --> 03:52.666
WEEK THAT THE U.S. WAS PREPARED

03:52.666 --> 03:56.403
TO SEND THE AID DIRECTLY TO

03:56.403 --> 03:56.570
KURDISTAN.

03:56.570 --> 03:57.604
THEY ARE COORDINATING THIS WITH

03:57.604 --> 03:57.771
BAGHDAD.

03:57.771 --> 03:59.372
THEY ARE NOT BYPASSING THE

03:59.372 --> 04:00.874
FEDERAL GOVERNMENT IN BAGHDAD.

04:00.874 --> 04:02.609
THEY’RE NOT CUTTING A SEPARATE

04:02.609 --> 04:03.944
DEAL WITH KURDISTAN, IF YOU

04:03.944 --> 04:04.244
LIKE.

04:04.244 --> 04:05.278
BUT THEY ARE SENDING ARMS.

04:05.278 --> 04:06.646
IT’S MY UNDERSTANDING THAT SOME

04:06.646 --> 04:08.148
HAVE ALREADY ARRIVED.

04:08.148 --> 04:09.116
>> Sreenivasan: LIZ SLY OF THE

04:09.116 --> 04:10.450
"WASHINGTON POST" JOINING US

04:10.450 --> 04:11.818
HAVE A SKYPE FROM IRAQ, THANKS

04:11.818 --> 04:12.552
SO MUCH.

04:12.552 --> 04:13.954
>> Reporter: THANK YOU.

04:13.954 --> 04:14.387
>> Sreenivasan: IN TEXAS TODAY,

04:14.387 --> 04:15.455
GOVERNOR RICK PERRY SAID HE IS

04:15.455 --> 04:16.556
INNOCENT OF ANY WRONGDOING.

04:16.556 --> 04:17.491
YESTERDAY, A GRAND JURY IN

04:17.491 --> 04:18.525
AUSTIN INDICTED THE PRESIDENTIAL

