TO 5:00 A.M. CURFEW IN FERGUSON

05:02.602 --> 05:05.772
TO TRY TO END THE VIOLENCE

05:05.772 --> 05:06.106
THERE.

05:06.106 --> 05:06.439
FOLLOWING THE FATAL SHOOTING

05:06.439 --> 05:09.776
OF A WEEK AGO OF AN UNARMED

05:09.776 --> 05:10.443
AFRICAN AMERICAN TEENAGER.

