SOME STORE OWNERS

05:21.454 --> 05:22.389
COMPLAINED THE POLICE, ACCUSED

05:22.389 --> 05:23.390
OF USING EXCESSIVE FORCE EARLIER

05:23.390 --> 05:24.324
IN THE WEEK DID NOT DO ENOUGH TO

05:24.324 --> 05:28.728
STOP THE LOOTERS LAST NIGHT.

05:28.728 --> 05:29.729
TURNING NOW BACK OVERSEAS

05:29.729 --> 05:30.497
TENSIONS REMAIN HIGH ALONG THE

05:30.497 --> 05:31.765
BORDER BETWEEN UKRAINE AND

05:31.765 --> 05:33.033
RUSSIA, AFTER REPORTS YESTERDAY

05:33.033 --> 05:33.033
THAT THE UKRAINIAN MILITARY HAD

05:33.033 --> 05:34.301
DESTROYED AN ARMED RUSSIAN

05:34.301 --> 05:40.640
CONVOY THAT HAD ENTERED UKRAINE.

05:40.640 --> 05:41.641
FOR MORE ABOUT THE CONFLICT AND

05:41.641 --> 05:42.709
EFFORTS TO END IT BEFORE IT

05:42.709 --> 05:43.743
ESCALATES FURTHER, WE ARE JOINED

05:43.743 --> 05:44.744
FROM MOSCOW VIA SKYPE BY JAMES

05:44.744 --> 05:45.612
MARSON OF THE WALL STREET

05:45.612 --> 05:49.182
JOURNAL.

05:49.182 --> 05:50.450
SO, YESTERDAY THERE WAS SOME

05:50.450 --> 05:51.318
CONFUSION ON WHETHER OR NOT THE

05:51.318 --> 05:52.819
EVENT HAPPENED AT ALL.

05:52.819 --> 05:54.955
THE UKRAINIANS SAY THEY DID AWAY

05:54.955 --> 05:56.923
WITH A RUSSIAN MILITARY CONVOY.

05:56.923 --> 05:58.425
THE RUSSIAN CALL IT A FANTASY.

05:58.425 --> 06:00.026
WHAT DO WE KNOW ABOUT IT?

06:00.026 --> 06:02.896
>> Reporter: THAT’S RIGHT.

06:02.896 --> 06:05.532
THIS CALL-UP OF ABOUT 20 ARMORED

06:05.532 --> 06:07.701
VEHICLE CROSSED OVER THE

06:07.701 --> 06:09.002
RUSSIAN-UKRAINIAN BORDER

06:09.002 --> 06:10.303
THURSDAY EVENING, SPOTTED BY TWO

06:10.303 --> 06:13.340
BRITISH REPORTERS.

06:13.340 --> 06:14.708
THEY SNUCK AROUND THE BORDER

06:14.708 --> 06:16.509
POST AND ENTERED UKRAINE.

06:16.509 --> 06:19.713
UKRAINE YESTERDAY SAID THAT IT

06:19.713 --> 06:23.216
HAD DESTROYED THIS ARMORED

06:23.216 --> 06:23.516
COLUMN.

06:23.516 --> 06:26.086
RUSSIA DISMISSED THIS AS A

06:26.086 --> 06:26.253
FANTASY.

06:26.253 --> 06:27.621
AND UKRAINE HAS SO FAR PROVIDED

06:27.621 --> 06:32.525
NO PICTURES OF THIS.

06:32.525 --> 06:34.861
IT ROYALED THE MARKET BECAUSE

06:34.861 --> 06:36.696
EVERYONE WAS FEARFUL THE

06:36.696 --> 06:37.664
DESTRUCTION OF THE COLUMN WOULD

06:37.664 --> 06:41.568
LEAD TO A WIDER CONFLICT IN

06:41.568 --> 06:42.736
RUSSIA AND UKRAINE.

06:42.736 --> 06:45.138
BUT IN FACT, TODAY, UKRAINE HAS

06:45.138 --> 06:46.473
TRIED TO PLAY IT DAY SAYING THIS

06:46.473 --> 06:48.942
IS QUITE A REGULAR OCCURRENCE,

06:48.942 --> 06:50.677
THAT RUSSIA KEEPS SEND THESE

06:50.677 --> 06:52.312
COLUMNS ACROSS.

06:52.312 --> 06:52.812
>> Sreenivasan: WHAT’S IN

06:52.812 --> 06:54.948
THEIR INTEREST TO MAKE THIS UP?

06:54.948 --> 06:56.583
>> Reporter: WELL, UKRAINE,

06:56.583 --> 06:58.418
OBVIOUSLY, WANTS TO MAKE IT SEEM

06:58.418 --> 07:00.120
LIKE IT WAS HAVING MILITARY

07:00.120 --> 07:01.655
SUCCESS AGAINST THE SEPARATISTS.

07:01.655 --> 07:02.589
IT DOESN’T WANT TO LOOK LIKE

07:02.589 --> 07:03.923
IT’S EASY FOR THE RUSSIANS TO

07:03.923 --> 07:07.394
SEND WEAPONS AND MEN INTO THE

07:07.394 --> 07:07.494
EAST.

07:07.494 --> 07:10.130
UKRAINE HAS BEEN FIGHTING THIS

07:10.130 --> 07:11.998
PRO-RUSSIAN INSURGENCY FOR

07:11.998 --> 07:12.799
AROUND FOUR MONTHS.

07:12.799 --> 07:14.100
IT’S BEEN HAVING SIGNIFICANT

07:14.100 --> 07:15.669
SUCCESSES IN RECENT WEEKS.

07:15.669 --> 07:17.270
IT’S MANAGED TO PUSH THE REBELS

07:17.270 --> 07:18.772
OUT OF A LOT OF TOWNS AND

07:18.772 --> 07:20.340
CITIES, AND THEY WANT TO KEEP

07:20.340 --> 07:21.608
THAT MOMENTUM GOING.

07:21.608 --> 07:22.442
>> Sreenivasan: WHAT ABOUT

07:22.442 --> 07:23.810
THAT AID CONVOY?

07:23.810 --> 07:24.978
WE’VE SEEN THOSE PICTURES OF

07:24.978 --> 07:25.912
THOSE HUNDREDS OF TRUCKS THAT

07:25.912 --> 07:27.447
ARE WAITING ON THE BORDER.

07:27.447 --> 07:29.783
ARE THEY ANY CLOSER TO GETTING

07:29.783 --> 07:29.916
THROUGH?

07:29.916 --> 07:30.784
>> Reporter: THEY SEEM TO BE

07:30.784 --> 07:33.820
STUCK ON THE BORDER AT THE

07:33.820 --> 07:34.054
MOMENT.

07:34.054 --> 07:34.921
THEY’RE PARKED UP IN A FIELD A

07:34.921 --> 07:36.556
FEW MILES FROM THE BORDER

07:36.556 --> 07:36.723
CROSSING.

07:36.723 --> 07:38.958
THE UKRAINIANS SAY THEY’RE

07:38.958 --> 07:40.627
WAITING FOR PAPERWORK WHICH WILL

07:40.627 --> 07:41.461
ALLOW THEM TO CROSS.

07:41.461 --> 07:45.999
THE RUSSIANS SAY THE UKRAINE

07:45.999 --> 07:48.768
RANS ARE NOT ALLOWING THEM TO GO

07:48.768 --> 07:48.868
ACROSS.

07:48.868 --> 07:51.771
THERE’S A LOT OF FINGER

07:51.771 --> 07:51.971
POINTING.

07:51.971 --> 07:56.476
UKRAINE IS SENDING THEIR OWN AID

07:56.476 --> 07:58.211
COLUMN, SO THERE ARE A LOT OF

07:58.211 --> 08:00.814
PEOPLE IN BESIEGED TOWNS WAITING

08:00.814 --> 08:02.415
FOR AID AND NOT RECEIVING IT.

08:02.415 --> 08:03.883
>> Sreenivasan: ANY ADVANCING

08:03.883 --> 08:05.051
ON THE DIPLOMATIC FRONT?

