>> THE DIPLOMATIC FRONT WAS

08:07.087 --> 08:09.022
FROZEN FOR A VERY LONG TIME BUT

08:09.022 --> 08:11.057
NOW IT APPEARS TO BE COMING BACK

08:11.057 --> 08:11.825
TO LIFE.

