THE FINNISH PRESIDENT WAS IN

08:13.626 --> 08:14.661
RUSSIA YESTERDAY MEETING

08:14.661 --> 08:15.395
VLADIMIR PUTIN.

08:15.395 --> 08:18.365
TODAY, HE IS IN UKRAINE, MEETING

08:18.365 --> 08:21.201
THE UKRAINIAN PRESIDENT.

08:21.201 --> 08:23.536
TOMORROW, THE FRENCH, GERMAN,

08:23.536 --> 08:24.904
UKRAINIAN, AND RUSSIAN FOREIGN

08:24.904 --> 08:26.606
MINISTERS WILL NEAT IN BERLIN.

08:26.606 --> 08:28.742
THERE SEEMS TO BE A CONCERTED

08:28.742 --> 08:29.909
DIPLOMATIC PUSH TO FIND A

08:29.909 --> 08:30.710
RESOLUTION HERE.

08:30.710 --> 08:31.945
NOW, IT COULD BE DIFFICULT TO

08:31.945 --> 08:34.514
FIND THAT RESOLUTION.

08:34.514 --> 08:36.783
UKRAINE HAS BEEN PUSHED WITH ITS

08:36.783 --> 08:40.453
MILITARY OPERATIONS AS IT SEEMS

08:40.453 --> 08:43.690
SOFEEL IT CAN PUSH THE REBELS

08:43.690 --> 08:43.790
OUT.

